According to the theory, they had argued about this which caused them to get lost in the jungle. At some point, Kris got so angry that she purposely pushed Lisanne to her death. Afterwards, it's possible that she couldn't live with herself and so, she just wandered around until she finally died of exhaustion, hunger, and thirst. 
